node.text:
Here are some of my all time favourite workouts I've been doing at home lately ! If you try this workout let me know know if it helps you 💗 
Skipping for 2 minutes - 3 sets
Jumping squats - 3 sets 10 reps 
Donkey kicks - 3 sets 10 reps 
Elbow to hands plank - 3 sets 10 reps 
Back lunges - 3 sets 10 reps 
Flute bridge - 4 sets 15 reps 
Side to side plank dips - 3 sets 12 reps 
Planking - hold 45 seconds 3 sets 
Squat with back leg kick - 3 sets 13 reps 
Curtesy lunges - 3 sets 10 reps 
Laying side  bent leg raises with resistance band - 12 reps each leg 3 sets

node.title: Home body and booty workout routine 💪🏽
